The paper focuses on predicting emotional impact in movies using image, audio, and face-based features computed using pre-trained neural networks. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Multimedia (cs.MM), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Sound and Music Computing (cs.SD), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Among these, cs.MM and cs.CV are the most likely categories as they directly relate to the use of visual and audio features in the paper.
